    No Inherent Mandate from the "Code": From your perspective of the universe as "potential" and "vibration," there's no inherent "law" in the universe's code that says "humans shall not steal" or "all humans have freedom of speech." These are human inventions, albeit often highly beneficial ones for human coexistence.\par
